# Cursor Plans File Commit Requirement

## Requirement

All plan files SHALL be committed to git following the standard commit message format requirements (see `git/commit-format.mdc`).

## Rationale

Committing plan files ensures:
- Plans are preserved in git history
- Planning decisions are traceable
- Audit trail exists for development approach
- Historical context is available for future reference
- Team members can review planning approaches

